snippet.title: Mini MSX - SEGA Master System Homebrew
snippet.description:
As part of a SMS Power Coding Cometition in 2021, this homage to the iconic MSX computer line includes a Pac-Man clone, a shoot'em up and a racing game. A pretty impressive little homebrew, innit?

Download link: https://www.smspower.org/Homebrew/MiniMSX-SMS
